{"article_id":"QUokDMl8WnZCaPGp","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The latest attempt","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"to repeal the Obama-era healthcare act","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"has failed after a dramatic night in the US Senate .","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"At least three Republicans","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"- John McCain , Susan Collins and Lisa Murkowski -","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"voted against the bill ,","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"which needed a simple majority","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"to pass .","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"President Donald Trump said","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"the three had `` let the American people down '' .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"The so-called `` skinny '' repeal ,","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"which would have scaled back some of the more controversial provisions ,","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"is the third failed attempt","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"to repeal Obamacare .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"It would have resulted in 16 million people losing their health insurance by 2026 ,","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"with insurance premiums increasing by 20 % ,","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"according to the Congressional Budget Office","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"( CBO ) .","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"The vote was delayed","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"after Senate Republicans kept a procedural vote open before the actual Obamacare vote","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"while they attempted to persuade their members to vote for the repeal .","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"Vice President Mike Pence was seen talking to Mr McCain for more than 20 minutes .","depth":5},{"id":22,"text":"But Mr McCain then approached a group of Democrats ,","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"who appeared happy to see him .","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"The bill was eventually voted down by 51 votes to 49 in the Republican-dominated Senate .","depth":4},{"id":25,"text":"Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell , a Republican , described the result as a `` disappointing moment '' .","depth":5},{"id":26,"text":"Democrat Chuck Schumer said","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"his party was relieved","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"that millions of people would retain their healthcare .","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"A dagger in Trump 's plans","depth":3},{"id":30,"text":"- BBC North America Correspondent Anthony Zurcher","depth":3},{"id":31,"text":"The arc of history is long ,","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"but it bends towards revenge .","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"Just over two years after candidate Donald Trump mocked John McCain 's Vietnam War record ,","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"noting","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"that he prefers heroes `` who were n't captured '' ,","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"the Arizona senator stuck a dagger in President Trump 's healthcare reform plans .","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"There were gasps","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"when Mr McCain ,","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"after being furiously lobbied by Vice-President Mike Pence ,","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"joined two other Republican senators","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"in voting against the so-called `` skinny '' repeal plan ,","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"considered the bare minimum","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"Senate Republicans could agree on .","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"Instead of a big step","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"toward becoming law","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"- either in its skinny form or after further negotiations with the House of Representatives -","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"the future of Obamacare repeal has been thrown into doubt .","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"The reality is , for now , there is no minimum level of change","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"on which Senate Republicans can agree .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"They either have to work with Democrats","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"or resign themselves","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"to stalemate","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"and move on to other topics , like taxes or infrastructure spending .","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"It will take some time for the scale of this late-night Senate drama to sink in .","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"No one really expected Mr McCain to be the decisive vote ,","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"but the man","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"who once had a reputation as a Republican `` maverick '' ,","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"now facing a dire brain cancer diagnosis ,","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"had at least one more surprise in his pocket .","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"The bill","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"- officially known as the Health Care Freedom Act -","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"would have eliminated parts of Obamacare","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"- the Affordable Care Act -","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"including the individual mandate","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"requiring all Americans to have health insurance coverage","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"or pay a fine ,","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"and the employer mandate ,","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"which requires the same of companies with 50 employees or more .","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"It also would have temporarily repealed a tax on medical devices , defund the US women 's group Planned Parenthood for a year","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"and provide more money to community health centres ,","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"as well as given states more flexibility","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"in complying with Obamacare regulations .","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"But the pared-down measure would have left much of Obamacare untouched ,","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"including the expansion of Medicaid , a government health programme for the poor","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"that faced deep cuts in earlier proposals .","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"A requirement","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"that all insurance plans cover essential health benefits ,","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"federal subsidies","depth":14},{"id":79,"text":"to help consumers pay for insurance","depth":14},{"id":80,"text":"as well as taxes on wealthy Americans","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"also would have remained in place .","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"The stripped down bill came after earlier Senate defeats for proposals","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"to replace Obamacare","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"and then to partially repeal it .","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"Sen McCain said","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"he had voted against the skinny repeal","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"because it did not amount to meaningful reform","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"and would not have improved care for Americans .","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"He added","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"that House Speaker Paul Ryan 's assurance","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"that the House would be willing to send the bill for further consideration by committee","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"`` did not ease my concern","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"that this shell of a bill could be taken up","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"and passed at any time '' .","depth":13},{"id":95,"text":"There are not thought to be any further plans for a new bill","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"to repeal Obamacare","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"because the skinny repeal was seen as the only measure","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"Republicans could get through Congress .","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"However , lawmakers could revive the issue","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"and take it up later in the year .","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"Following the vote ,","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"President Trump tweeted :","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"`` As I said from the beginning ,","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"let ObamaCare implode ,","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"then deal . ''","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"Mr Trump 's position on healthcare reform has varied","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"- he has spoken out at various points for Obamacare being repealed , repealed","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"and replaced ,","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"or being allowed to collapse by itself .","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"In his statement , Mr McCain said","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"Obamacare was in a state of `` collapse '' ,","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"with healthcare premiums `` skyrocketing ''","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"and providers `` fleeing the marketplace '' .","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"He criticised the way","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"Obamacare had been passed by Democrats","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"using their Obama-era majority","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"and called for senators to `` return to the correct way","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"of legislating '' with input from both parties .","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"`` We must do the hard work","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"our citizens expect of us","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"and deserve , ''","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"But Texas Senator Ted Cruz insisted","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"the fight was not over .","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"`` Mark my words ,","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"this journey is not yet done , ''","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"he said .","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":255,"left":156,"right":254,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":145,"right":155,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":145,"left":141,"right":144,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":141,"left":137,"right":140,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":137,"left":130,"right":136,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":129,"right":2,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":129,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":136,"left":134,"right":135,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":134,"left":131,"right":133,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":131,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":133,"left":